  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1457",
  "title": "Replace our RangeSlider with airbnb/rheostat",
  "body": "For now, there's no way we are gonna make a better Slider that airbnb/rheostat. So the best option is to make our RangeSlider be a thin wrapper on top of airbnb/rheostat and make it look good, consistent (#1456).\n\nWe also discussed that we could maybe just not include a default slider, but for our set of widgets that would look pretty weird to not have a RangeSlider widget by default. Even if connecting one is very easy.\n",
